      "text": "// languageFor returns the tree-sitter Language for a grammar name, or nil if\n// the grammar is not registered.\nfunc languageFor(name string) *tree_sitter.Language {\n\tif f, ok := grammars[name]; ok {\n\t\treturn f()\n\t}\n\treturn nil\n}",
